Starting new angular project
ng new receipeApp - select CSS - no routing

Adding bootstrap locally for this project
-> npm --install save bootstrap@3

Go to angular.json find "styles and add bootstrap.min.css"  after npm install, it will be found under "node_modules" directory.

 "styles": [
              "node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css",
              "src/styles.css"
            ]
            
